"In the *Barcode* section, select the :guilabel:`Barcode Scanner` option. Be "
"sure to click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:22
msgid "Barcode nomenclature"
msgstr "تسمية الباركود"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:24
msgid ""
"Most retail products use EAN-13 barcodes, also known as Global Trade "
"Identification Numbers (GTIN). To create a new |GTIN| for a product, a "
"company must have a GS1 Company Prefix. See :doc:`GS1 nomenclature <../"
"operations/gs1_nomenclature>` for more information about using this system."
msgstr ""
"تستخدم معظم منتجات التجزئة باركودات EAN-13، المعروفة أيضاً باسم أرقام التعريف "
"التجارية العالمية (GTIN). لإنشاء |GTIN| جديد لمنتج، يجب أن يكون لدى الشركة "
"بادئة شركة GS1. راجع :doc:`تسمية GS1 <../operations/gs1_nomenclature>` لمزيد "
"من المعلومات حول استخدام هذا النظام."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:28
msgid ""
"Odoo supports using any string as a barcode, so users can also create custom "
"internal references for barcode scanners. See the :doc:`Default nomenclature "
"<../operations/barcode_nomenclature>` to learn about optional conventions "
"around barcodes and default values in Odoo."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/setup/software.rst:32
