#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:27
msgid ""
"Once logged into the Starshipit account, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Pickup address`, and fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Pickup address`. Ensure this field matches the warehouse "
