msgstr "وحدة Starshipit Shipping في وحدة تطبيقات Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:104
msgid "Configure a Starshipit delivery method"
msgstr "تكوين طريقة تسليم Starshipit"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:106
msgid ""
"Once installed, activate the feature by going to :menuselection:`Inventory --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`. Under the :guilabel:`Shipping Connectors` "
"section, activate the :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector` option."
msgstr ""
"بمجرد التثبيت، قم بتنشيط الميزة بالانتقال إلى :menuselection:`المخزون --> "
"الإعدادات --> الإعدادات`. ضمن قسم :guilabel:`موصلات الشحن`، قم بتنشيط "
"خيار :guilabel:`موصل Starshipit`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:110
msgid ""
"After activating :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector`, click "
"the :guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping Methods` link below the listed connector. "
"Once on the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` page, click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"بعد تفعيل :guilabel:`Starshipit Connector`، انقر على "
"رابط :guilabel:`Starshipit Shipping Methods` أسفل الموصل المدرج. بمجرد "
"الوصول إلى صفحة :guilabel:`طرق التسليم`، انقر على :guilabel:`إنشاء`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Methods` can also be accessed by going "
"to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery --> Delivery "
"Methods`."
msgstr ""
"يمكن أيضًا الوصول إلى :guilabel:`طرق التسليم` بالانتقال "
"إلى :menuselection:`المخزون --> التكوين --> التسليم --> طرق التسليم`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:118
msgid ""
"Configure a Starshipit delivery method in Odoo by filling out the fields on "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Methods` form as follows:"
msgstr ""
"قم بتكوين طريقة تسليم Starshipit في Odoo من خلال ملء الحقول في "
"نموذج :guilabel:`طرق التسليم` كما يلي:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Delivery Method`: type `Starshipit`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`طريقة التسليم`: اكتب `Starshipit`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Starshipit` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ":guilabel:`المزود`: حدد :guilabel:`Starshipit` من القائمة المنسدلة."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:123
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Product`: assign or create the delivery product that "
"will appear on the sales order line when the cost of shipping is computed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`منتج التوصيل`: قم بتعيين أو إنشاء منتج التوصيل الذي سيظهر في بند "
"أمر البيع عند حساب تكلفة الشحن."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:127
msgid ""
"The fields discussed in this section are specific to configuring Starshipit. "
"For more information about the other fields, refer to :doc:`../"
"setup_configuration`."
msgstr ""
"الحقول التي تمت مناقشتها في هذا القسم خاصة بتكوين Starshipit. لمزيد من "
"المعلومات حول الحقول الأخرى، راجع :doc:`../setup_configuration`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:130
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Starshipit Configuration` tab, fill out these fields:"
msgstr "في علامة التبويب :guilabel:`تكوين Starshipit`، املأ هذه الحقول:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Starshipit API Key`: enter the :abbr:`API (Application "
"Programming Interface)` key :ref:`obtained from Starshipit <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/star-api>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`مفتاح API الخاص بـ Starshipit`: أدخل مفتاح :abbr:`واجهة برمجة "
"التطبيقات` :ref:`الذي تم الحصول عليه من Starshipit <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/star-api>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Starshipit Subscription Key`: enter the subscription key obtained "
"from the same place as the :ref:`API key <inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"api>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`مفتاح اشتراك Starshipit`: أدخل مفتاح الاشتراك الذي تم الحصول عليه "
"من نفس مكان :ref:`مفتاح API <inventory/shipping_receiving/star-api>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:136
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Origin Address`: Enter the address where products are shipped "
"from. This field is crucial for calculating shipping rates "
"and :ref:`generating shipping labels <inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"label>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`عنوان المنشأ`: أدخل العنوان الذي يتم شحن المنتجات منه. هذا الحقل "
"بالغ الأهمية لحساب أسعار الشحن و:ref:`إنشاء ملصقات الشحن <inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/star-label>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:139
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Package Type`: Set a default package type to include the "
"weight of the empty package when automatically calculating shipping rates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`نوع الطرد الافتراضي`: قم بتعيين نوع طرد افتراضي لتضمين وزن الطرد "
"الفارغ عند حساب أسعار الشحن تلقائياً."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:143
msgid ""
"To set a default package type, the *Packages* feature **must** be enabled "
"in :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Settings`."
msgstr ""
"لتعيين نوع طرد افتراضي، **يجب** تمكين ميزة *الطرود* "
"في :menuselection:`المخزون --> الإعدادات --> الإعدادات`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:146
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` icon at the "
"top of the page to save the changes."
msgstr ""
"انقر على أيقونة :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(حفظ يدويًا)` في أعلى "
"الصفحة لحفظ التغييرات."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:148
msgid ""
"To load the newly configured shipping products, click :guilabel:`Select a "
"service linked to your starshipit account` at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Starshipit Configuration` tab, and a :guilabel:`Choose "
"Starshipit Shipping Service` pop-up window appears. In "
"the :guilabel:`Delivery Service` field, select the desired shipping service "
"for deliveries and returns from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"لتحميل منتجات الشحن المكونة حديثًا، انقر على :guilabel:`اختر خدمة مرتبطة "
"بحساب starshipit الخاص بك` في أسفل علامة تبويب :guilabel:`تكوين Starshipit`، "
"وستظهر نافذة منبثقة بعنوان :guilabel:`اختر خدمة شحن Starshipit`. في "
"حقل :guilabel:`خدمة التسليم`، حدد خدمة الشحن المطلوبة للتسليمات والمرتجعات "
"من القائمة المنسدلة."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:154
msgid ""
"The list of services shown during initial configuration may be incomplete. "
"Starshipit determines service availability based on shipment details such as "
"the destination address and package weight, which are not yet available at "
"this stage. To select from the full list of services available for a "
"specific order, use the :guilabel:`Get more delivery methods` option "
"directly from the sales order. See :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/star-"
"label` for details."
msgstr ""
"قد تكون قائمة الخدمات المعروضة أثناء التكوين الأولي غير مكتملة. يحدد "
"Starshipit توفر الخدمة بناءً على تفاصيل الشحنة مثل عنوان الوجهة ووزن الطرد، "
"والتي لا تكون متاحة بعد في هذه المرحلة. للاختيار من القائمة الكاملة للخدمات "
"المتاحة لطلب معين، استخدم خيار :guilabel:`الحصول على المزيد من طرق التسليم` "
"مباشرة من أمر البيع. راجع :ref:`inventory/shipping_receiving/star-label` "
"للحصول على التفاصيل."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:160
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` and the selected delivery service populates in "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` and :guilabel:`Starshipit Service Code` "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"انقر على :guilabel:`تأكيد` وستظهر خدمة التسليم المحددة في "
"حقلي :guilabel:`طريقة الشحن` و :guilabel:`رمز خدمة Starshipit`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:163
msgid "Sample of a Starshipit shipping product configured in Odoo:"
msgstr "نموذج لمنتج شحن Starshipit تم تكوينه في Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/starshipit_shipping.rst:0
